  <title>LECTURER IN PUBLIC HEALTH MEDICINE – fixed term contract (July 2020-July 2022)</title>
  <link>https://www.ub.bw/connect/job-opportunities/lecturer-public-health-medicine-%E2%80%93-fixed-term-contract-july-2020-july-2022</link>
  <description>&lt;span class="field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden"&gt;LECTURER IN PUBLIC HEALTH MEDICINE – fixed term contract (July 2020-July 2022)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="field field--name-uid field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden"&gt;&lt;span lang="" about="https://www.ub.bw/user/2085" typeof="schema:Person" property="schema:name" datatype="" xml:lang=""&gt;maribek&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="field field--name-created field--type-created field--label-hidden"&gt;Mon, 27/07/2020 - 11:45&lt;/span&gt;

  &lt;div class="field field--name-field-department field--type-entity-reference field--label-inline clearfix"&gt;
    &lt;div class="field__label"&gt;Department/Faculty&lt;/div&gt;
              &lt;div class="field__item"&gt;Family Medicine &amp; Public Health&lt;/div&gt;
