&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;VACANCY NO:  FM/FMPH 1/2020, LECTURER&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Duties:&lt;/strong&gt; The successful candidate will be expected to: &lt;strong&gt;(i) &lt;/strong&gt;teach undergraduate and graduate students; &lt;strong&gt;(ii)&lt;/strong&gt; conduct research; &lt;strong&gt;(iii) &lt;/strong&gt;provide clinical care in affiliated hospitals.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Requirements:&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;strong&gt;(i)&lt;/strong&gt; a Doctorate in Family Medicine or related discipline or; &lt;strong&gt;(ii)&lt;/strong&gt; a Master’s degree in Family Medicine and &lt;strong&gt;(iii)&lt;/strong&gt; a Bachelor of Medicine and Bachelor of surgery (MBBS or MBChB) or MO degree, with at least a 2.1 pass, or an equivalent degree which may be considered under special circumstances, and &lt;strong&gt;(iv)&lt;/strong&gt; must be registered with Botswana Health Professions Council as a specialist in Family Medicine; &lt;strong&gt;(v)&lt;/strong&gt; show evidence of engagement in research. University teaching experience will be considered an advantage.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Remuneration: &lt;/strong&gt;The University offers competitive salaries and benefits commensurate with experience and qualification&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;How to apply:&lt;/strong&gt; Applicants are to address the stated qualification and provide other information to assist the university determine their suitability for the position.  They should provide current CV’s (including telephone and e-mail), certified copies of educational certificates and transcripts, and THREE (3) reference letters.  Applicants should inform their referees to:  (i) Quote the position applied for and (ii) submit their references directly to the address below;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Human Resources Manager, Faculty of Medicine, Corner of Notwane and Mabuto Road, University of Botswana, Private Bag 00713 Gaborone, Botswana; or Email to nkangana@mopipi.ub.bw &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Hand delivered applications should be sent to Faculty of Medicine, &lt;strong&gt;UB Teaching Hospital, 3rd Floor, Office F 4003&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;NB:&lt;/strong&gt;  Only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.&lt;/p&gt;

